@node Main "NewHomerPrefs"

Short:        Preferences GUI for NewHomer
Author:       allan.tnt@post.tele.dk (Allan Rasmussen)
Uploader:     allan.tnt@post.tele.dk (Allan Rasmussen)
Version:      1.00 (23-Sep-2006)
Type:         util/misc/
Architecture: generic
Requires:     util/rexx/rxmui.lha util/libs/mui38usr.lha dev/mui/MCC_Lamp.lha dev/mui/MCC_NList*.lha
Url:          http://home19.inet.tele.dk/acme/

This is a Preferences GUI for NewHomer 1.89c
It will probably also work with other versions.

It is written in ARexx and requires RxMUI
http://alfie.altervista.org/downloads/rxmui.lha

 This guide is compiled of comments from the original NewHomer.conf file, describing the settings.
 Please do also refer to Homer.guide and NewHomer.guide.

